<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>500 | Internal Server Error</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/home.css" /> <!-- or your main CSS -->
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #fff5f5;
      color: #3b1f1f;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .error-container {
      max-width: 500px;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
    }
    .error-container h1 {
      font-size: 5rem;
      margin: 0;
      color: #d6336c;
    }
    .error-container h2 {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .error-container p {
      margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #6a5151;
    }
    .home-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background: #d6336c;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 2rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }
    .home-btn:hover {
      background: #b81f53;
    }
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="error-container">
    <h1>500</h1>
    <h2>Something went wrong!</h2>
    <p>We're facing a little hiccup on our end. Our team has been notified and will fix it shortly.</p>
    <a href="/" class="home-btn">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
